<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    p {
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .otp-code {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      border: 2px solid #ddd;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Welcome, <%= user.name %>!</h2>

    <p>Thank you for signing up to CYANLMS. To activate your account, please enter the following 6-digit OTP:</p>

    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>

    <p>This OTP is valid for 5 minutes.</p>

    <p>We're excited to have you on board!  </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Sincerely,</p>
      <p>The LMS Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
